<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rtc\"><code>&lt;rtc&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>S\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>elemento HTML &lt;b&gt;</strong> representa um intervalo de texto estilísticamente diferente do texto normal, sem transmitir qualquer importância ou relevância. Ele é geralmente usado para destacar palavras-chaves em um resumo, nomes de produtos em um comentário ou outros vãos de texto cuja a apresentação típica seria negrito. Outro exemplo de seu uso é como marcação da frase principal de cada paragrafo de um artigo.</p>\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n <p><strong>Notas de Uso:</strong></p>\n <ul>\n  <li>Não confunda o elemento &lt;b&gt; com os elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a> ,&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a> . O elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a> representa um texto com importância, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a> coloca alguma ênfase no texto e o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a> representa o texto relevante. O elemento &lt;b&gt; não transmite essa informação semântica especial. Você deve usá-lo apenas quando os outros elementos citados não se encaixam na situação.</li>\n  <li>Também não é recomendado marcar títulos de cabeçalhos usando o elemento &lt;b&gt;. Para isso, use as tags <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> até <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. usando essas tags você terá liberdade de mudar o estilo padrão dos elementos e não ficará preso ao negrito do elemento &lt;b&gt;.</li>\n  <li>É uma boa prática usar o atributo de classe &lt;b&gt;, a fim de transmitir informação semântica adicional. Isso facilita o desenvolvimento de várias \"stylings\" de um documento web, sem a necessidade de alterar o seu código HTML.</li>\n  <li>Historicamente, o elemento &lt;b&gt; foi criado para fazer o texto ficar em negrito. Porém as informações de estilo ficou obsoleta desde o HTML4, de modo que significado da tag &lt;b&gt; foi alterado.</li>\n  <li>Se não a propósito semântico sobre o uso do elemento &lt;b&gt;, usar a propriedade css&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/CSS/font-weight\" title=\"font-weight\">font-weight</a> com algum volume seria uma escolha melhor para fazer o texto ficar em negrito.</li>\n </ul>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Content categories</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">phrasing content</a>, palpable content.</li>\n <li><dfn>Permitted content</dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">Phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Tag omission</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Permitted parent elements</dfn> Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a> Up to Gecko 1.9.2 (Firefox 4) inclusive, Firefox implements the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/span\" title=\"DOM/span\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a> interface for</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento só inclui os <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Este artigo descreve vários <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>níveis de texto<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>. Ele explica a utilização do elemento em um documento <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>HTML<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\nPalavras-chave são exibidas com o estilo padrão do elemento <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>, provavelmente em negrito.\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Este artigo descreve vários<strong> níveis de texto</strong>. Ele explica a utilização do elemento em um documento <strong>HTML</strong>.</p>\n<p>Palavras-chave são exibidas com o estilo padrão do elemento &lt;b&gt;, provavelmente em negrito.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificaçoes</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-b-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;b&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/text-level-semantics.html#the-b-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;b&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/present/graphics.html#h-15.2.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;b&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"navegadores_compatíveis","title":"Navegadores Compatíveis","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Recurso</th>\n    <th>Chrome</th>\n    <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n    <th>Opera</th>\n    <th>Safari</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Suporte Basico</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n <table class=\"compat-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <th>Recurso</th>\n    <th>Android</th>\n    <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n    <th>IE Mobile</th>\n    <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n    <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td>Suporte Basico</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td>1.0 (1.0)</td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n    <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja Também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outros elementos de transporte <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Text_level_semantics_conveying_elements\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">text-level semantics</a>: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rp\"><code>&lt;rp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/International/questions/qa-b-and-i-tags\" rel=\" noopener\">Using &lt;b&gt; and &lt;i&gt; elements (W3C)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"sect4\">\n </div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Navegadores Compatíveis","id":"navegadores_compatíveis"},{"text":"Veja Também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <b> representa um intervalo de texto estilísticamente diferente do texto normal, sem transmitir qualquer importância ou relevância. Ele é geralmente usado para destacar palavras-chaves em um resumo, nomes de produtos em um comentário ou outros vãos de texto cuja a apresentação típica seria negrito. Outro exemplo de seu uso é como marcação da frase principal de cada paragrafo de um artigo.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"b","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<b>: The Bring Attention To element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"b","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<b> : l'élément portant à l'attention","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<b>: 注目付け要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<b>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"b","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<b>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<b>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/b","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/b/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b","title":"<b>"}],"pageTitle":"<b> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}